realtimeweb.businesssearch.main
Class CoordinateLocation

Object
  realtimeweb.businesssearch.main.CoordinateLocation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Location
public class CoordinateLocation
extends Object
implements Location

A Location that is given by a latitude and longitude. You can also specify an accuracy for the location, and an altitude (and the accuracy of that altitude).

Author:
acbart
